title: Can't watch replay
body: So I can't watch my replay after I download the part I want it, it just show white paper. Can someone help solve it?

replies.body: If that replay is from a match that took place on an earlier patch, it won't be viewable anymore on the current patch. Those replays run partially off the patch that the game was played on so once a patch drops and files change, that replay won't be able to find the files it was originally using and won't work.
Hello there, thanks for the reply. But it's seem like it was this patch. I downloaded last night and highlighted the parts I want but it's just show up as a white note paper.
